text: ve donon daravaaze kee or jhapate aur us stree ne usaka kurta peechhe se phaad daala. daravaaze par donon ne us stree ke pati ko upasthit paaya. vah bolee, "jo koee tumhaaree gharavaalee ke saath bura iraada kare, usaka badala isake siva aur kya hoga ki use bandee banaaya jae ya phir koee dukhad yaatana dee jae
